Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:24.14,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,妳嘟著嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:31.03,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,表情裡看出了小算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:36.32,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,因為那份若即若離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:46.25,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,被妳藏到了口袋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:53.17,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,回憶是黑白照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:58.39,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,為它添上顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:06.94,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,再一次來到我的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:12.15,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,我五彩斑斕的寶貝兒女
